---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const breadcrumbs = [
  { name: 'Home', url: '/' },
  { name: 'Service Providers', url: '/for-providers' },
  { name: 'Specialty Facilities', url: '/for-providers/specialty-facilities' }
];
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Specialty Facilities on BreederHQ Marketplace"
  description="List your hydrotherapy pool, underwater treadmill, rehab/PT space, sensory/calming room, scent work facility, fitness/conditioning space, or whelping/neonatal room on the BreederHQ Marketplace. $5/month, no commissions."
  breadcrumbs={breadcrumbs}
>
<main>
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-fuchsia-50 to-white py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <div class="text-4xl mb-4">✨</div>
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 mb-6">Specialty Facilities</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">
        Hydrotherapy, underwater treadmills, rehab and PT, sensory rooms, fitness and conditioning spaces, and whelping or neonatal rooms.
        Owners and pros are searching the BreederHQ Marketplace for purpose-built specialty space.
      </p>
      <a href="https://accounts.breederhq.com/register?intent=provider_marketplace" class="bg-fuchsia-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-fuchsia-600">
        List Your Specialty Facility
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">What you can list</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-stone-200">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Water &amp; Therapy</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-2">
            <li>Hydrotherapy and swim spaces</li>
            <li>Underwater treadmills</li>
            <li>Land treadmills for conditioning</li>
            <li>Rehab and physical therapy spaces</li>
            <li>Recovery rooms with non-slip flooring</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-stone-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-stone-200">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Specialty Spaces</h3>
          <ul class="text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-2">
            <li>Sensory and calming rooms</li>
            <li>Scent work facilities</li>
            <li>Fitness and conditioning rooms</li>
            <li>Whelping and neonatal spaces</li>
            <li>Private session and pro-only options</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-stone-50">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Why it works for specialty facility owners</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">🎯</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Highly targeted demand</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">People searching for hydrotherapy or rehab know exactly what they need. They're ready to book the right space.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">👨‍⚕️</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Show your supervision level</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">List self-serve, provider-supervised, or pro-only options. Owners and rehab pros immediately see if your space fits their case.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-2xl mb-3">📋</div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Clear protocols</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Cleaning protocol, intake forms, and emergency contact protocol surface in your listing. Builds trust before the first session.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Your listing includes</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-fuchsia-700 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Subtype, species supported, supervision level</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-fuchsia-700 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Equipment list, professional-required flag, pro-only or self-serve</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-fuchsia-700 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Climate control, private session, water-based facility</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-fuchsia-700 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Heated pool, ramp, life jackets, towels, force dryer</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-fuchsia-700 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Cleaning protocol, emergency contact protocol, intake form</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-stone-50 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-fuchsia-700 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Per-session or per-hour pricing, photos, inquiry-to-book</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-6 text-center">
        Specialty facilities use a contact-to-book workflow: owners and pros send an inquiry, you confirm scheduling and arrange payment directly.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-fuchsia-900 to-fuchsia-800">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-white"><span class="line-through opacity-60 text-2xl">$5/mo</span> Free during early access</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-fuchsia-200 mb-3">No commissions. No per-session fees. Cancel anytime.</p>
      <p class="text-lg text-fuchsia-200 mb-8">Get your specialty facility in front of every owner and pro searching for hydrotherapy, rehab, or specialty work in your region.</p>
      <a href="https://accounts.breederhq.com/register?intent=provider_marketplace" class="bg-white text-fuchsia-800 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold hover:bg-fuchsia-50">
        List Your Specialty Facility
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
</BaseLayout>
